description: This common Sakura purrs with a rating of 34, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 34, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 8 for East, 1 for South, and Box for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
